LINK: https://datalemur.com/questions/sql-histogram-tweets

==> My approach:
WITH tweet_count AS (
SELECT user_id
     , COUNT(tweet_id) AS tweet_bucket
FROM tweets
WHERE DATE_PART('year', tweet_date) = 2022
GROUP BY user_id
)
SELECT tweet_bucket
     , COUNT(*) AS users_num
FROM tweet_count
GROUP BY tweet_bucket;
